==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Infarction
<hw>In*farc"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Infarce</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of stuffing or
filling;</def> <specif>Specifically:</specif> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>the
formation of an infarct; an overloading and obstruction of any organ or
vessel of the body; constipation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An infarct{2}; <as>as, a cardiac
<ex>infarction</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Infare</ent>⟦br⟧
